n_data <- nrow(cars_numeric) # number of rows 

test_index <- sample(1:n_data, # from 1 to the end of our data
                     size = n_data*0.2) 

test <- slice(cars_numeric, test_index)

train <- slice(cars_numeric, -test_index)


cars_train_pca <- prcomp(train,
                         center = T,
                         scale. = T,
                         rank. = 4)
